Kansas City Royals starting pitcher Edinson Volquez talks to the media during a news conference before batting practice for baseball's American League Championship Series Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015 in Kansas City, Mo. Volquez will start for the Royals as they face the Toronto Blue Jays in Game 1 tomorrow. (AP Photo/Charlie Riedel) Matt Slocum LEADING OFF: Blue Jays play at Royals in ALCS opener
